import React from 'react';
import {SidebarContainer, Icon, CloseIcon, SidebarWrapper, SidebarMenu, SidebarLinks,SideBtnWrap,SidebarRoute} from './SideBarElements'


const SideBar = ({toggle,isOpen}) => {
    console.log(toggle)
    return (
        <SidebarContainer isOpen={isOpen} onClick={toggle}>
            <Icon onClick={toggle}>
                <CloseIcon/>
            </Icon>
            <SidebarWrapper>
                <SidebarMenu>
                    <SidebarLinks to={'/about'}> About</SidebarLinks>
                    <SidebarLinks to={'/discover'}> Discover</SidebarLinks>
                    <SidebarLinks to={'/services'}> Services</SidebarLinks>
                    <SidebarLinks to={'/signUp'}> Sign Up</SidebarLinks>
                </SidebarMenu>
                <SideBtnWrap>
                    <SidebarRoute to={"/signin"}>Sign in</SidebarRoute>
                </SideBtnWrap>
            </SidebarWrapper>
        </SidebarContainer>
    )


}

export default SideBar
